page.title: 09TYPICAL DAY (2)
page.content: go out to play rounders in the summer or netball and football in the winter. From 14 30 to 14 45 we have another playtime. In our last session we might do history,science,geography,R.E.,or have a story until hometime at 15 40 I leave school and walk home. I get in at 16 00. I feed my cat,then watch television until I have my tea at 17 00. After tea I go out and play with my friends. We go cycling and play in the woods in a ruin barn until it gets dark. Then I go home and watch television until 21 00 when I go to bed.
